{"id":"8982","name":"App Limiter","tagline":"Limits use of certain apps for 5 minutes out of each hour","latest":"27050","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Set this shortcut to run when opening certain apps you want to spend less time using. When you open one these apps for the first time, you will have 5 minutes to open and close them as much as you want. After 5 minutes, a timer will go off and any new instances of the apps will automatically be switched to the Plantie focus app. After 1 hour, apps can be opened again.</p>\n<p>Optional: add \"Wait [X] seconds\" at the first step if you would like to be able to do something quick like respond to a message, but prevent prolonged screen time.</p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>2.0 - April 26, 2021, 5:01 p.m.</strong></p><p>Smarter notifications </p>"}